Car - Class in <Unnamed>
Class representing a single carr maintained within the priority queue database includes accessor and settors for all fields that are able to be changed externally Additionally, includes comparators for both price and mileage based data structures

CarTracker - Class in <Unnamed>
Class that serves as the user control over a priority queue based database of user defined cars the program supports a dynamically expanding number of cars as well as continued operation until the user explicitly decides to exit the program
